snippet.title: Lundum Creare - The Thrill of Hitting It Exact
snippet.description:
Have 72 hours to make a game but every time there's progress a new bug appears so have to debug the code to find it, then have to fight it while keeping my sanity and energy from getting too low.

Get this game at - https://jontopielski.itch.io/ludum-creare

It's Safe Up Here - https://youtu.be/kQ-qkcqj07k

Roseblight Demo - https://youtu.be/q4A0wl8edqA

Lasagna Boy - https://youtu.be/SeDB-rKKfzo
